net.tridentsdk.util

Class Pair<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.tridentsdk.util.Pair<K,V>

  • public abstract class Pair<K,V>
extends Object
    A pair of objects

    This class has no constructor. Rather, it has several different factory methods that instantiate internal implementations of the Pair. For most intents and purposes, one would use the mutable[XXX]() factory methods, depending on the context of usage.

    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
